---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Web Development – Onyx Labs"
  description="Interfaces built for AI-native workflows."
>
  <section class="content-main">
    <div class="container shell">
      <div class="content-layout">
        <div>
          <div class="content-kicker">Web Development</div>
          <h1 class="content-heading">Interfaces built for AI-native workflows.</h1>
          <p class="content-lede">
            We craft fast, modern web experiences for AI-backed products — from marketing sites to
            complex internal tools.
          </p>
          <div class="content-tags">
            <span class="tag">Product UIs</span>
            <span class="tag">Internal Tools</span>
            <span class="tag">Marketing Sites</span>
            <span class="tag">Design Systems</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="content-panel">
          <h3>What we care about</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Speed and responsiveness, even with heavy AI workloads.</li>
            <li>Clear, legible interfaces for complex decisions.</li>
            <li>Accessible, inclusive experiences by default.</li>
            <li>Maintainable, documented codebases your team can own.</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="content-panel">
          <h3>AI product interfaces</h3>
          <p>
            We design and implement web interfaces where AI is a co-pilot, not a black box —
            surfacing context, uncertainty, and controls.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Search, summarization, and exploration interfaces.</li>
            <li>Copilot-style assistants embedded in workflows.</li>
            <li>Human-in-the-loop review and approval flows.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="content-panel">
          <h3>Design systems & front-end foundations</h3>
          <p>
            We help you establish reusable components, patterns, and documentation so you can ship
            consistently over time.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Component libraries tuned to your brand.</li>
            <li>Design tokens and responsive layout systems.</li>
            <li>Developer docs and examples your team can extend.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-section">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div>
            <div class="section-title">Example engagements</div>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              You can bring us in for net-new builds or to refactor critical flows in existing
              products.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">Marketing</div>
            <div class="card-title">AI product marketing sites</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              High-conversion marketing and documentation sites that clearly explain your AI
              product.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">Product</div>
            <div class="card-title">Dashboard & workflow UIs</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              Data-rich dashboards and workflow tools that expose AI output safely and clearly.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">Systems</div>
            <div class="card-title">Design system build-out</div>
            <p class="card-body-text">
              A pragmatic design system implemented in code, with docs and examples.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
